WEBVTT

00:02.309 --> 00:04.276
Beato Michaeli archangelo,

00:04.344 --> 00:06.946
beato Ioanni baptistae,

00:07.013 --> 00:10.449
sanctis apostalies
Petro et paolo.

00:10.517 --> 00:12.651
Confiteor deo...

00:15.956 --> 00:17.656
Faye. Charlie.

00:17.724 --> 00:19.024
Dr. Lightman.

00:20.026 --> 00:23.362
I'm sorry about,
um, Dave and sue.

00:23.430 --> 00:26.765
Yeah, to lose their son and
then die in a car crash.

00:26.833 --> 00:29.101
Life is so unfair.

00:29.169 --> 00:31.103
Beato Michaeli archangelo,

00:31.171 --> 00:35.708
sanctis apostalie
Petro et paolo.

00:37.043 --> 00:38.410
It's time.

00:39.612 --> 00:41.380
It's about time
they killed this monster

00:41.448 --> 00:43.015
for what he did to our nephew.

00:43.083 --> 00:46.618
Death by injection's too good for
this unrepentant son of a bitch.

00:46.686 --> 00:49.488
Ah. Well,
what can I say?

00:49.556 --> 00:52.558
Confiteor deo omnipotenti,

00:52.625 --> 00:56.495
beatae Mariae semper virgini.

01:03.003 --> 01:04.769
You ok?

01:04.837 --> 01:07.106
Ah, don't answer that.

01:07.173 --> 01:09.208
I'll shut up now.

01:09.275 --> 01:13.579
...Omnipotenti, beatae
Mariae semper virgini,

01:13.646 --> 01:16.515
beato Michaeli archangelo.

